<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1048760>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dorsal views of preserved holotypes of (a) Uroplatus fotsivava sp. nov. and (c) U. kelirambo sp. nov., as well as (b, d) sulcal views of the everted hemipenes of the two species. Scale bars refer to the photos of the two specimens; hemipenis photos not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1048760/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

